query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('15.10',
'3d',
'64-bit',
'axiom-of-choice',
'dell',
'display',
'gui',
'numerical-linear-algebra',
'statistical-inference',
'text-processing',
'volume') AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000 group by t1.name;
